    This functions checks whether item's id is null, in which case item is 
    saved as a new DB record. Otherwise, existing record is updated. The new
    (for new items) or existing id is returned.
    
    \param ZfBlank_DbTable_SiteMenu $table save to different table (optional)
    \param boolean $recursion whether to save all descendants (subtree)
    \return mixed: item's ID.
